<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            background-color: #4f5ef1;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        p {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        h4 {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        td, th {
            padding: 8px 10px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        th {
            font-weight: 600;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ffffff44;
        }
        td {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ffffff22;
        }
        .order-details {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ffffff33;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #ffffff;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="message-sm">
            <h1>Your EduClarity Order ðŸ›’ is Confirmed!</h1>
            <p>And we're excited to help you achieve your goals! ðŸŽ‰</p>
        </div>
        <div class="course-info">
            <h4>Here's what you ordered:</h4>
            <div class="order-details">
                <span><strong>Order #:</strong> <%= order._id %></span>
                
                <span><strong>Order Date:</strong> <%= order.data %></span>
            </div>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Item</th>
                        <th>Qty</th>
                        <th>Cost</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td><%= order.name %></td>
                        <td>1</td>
                        <td>$<%= order.price %></td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                If you have any questions, please contact our support team at
                <a href="mailto:support@educlarity.com">support@educlarity.com</a>.
            </p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 EduClarity. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
